{% include 'components/header.njk' %}
<div class="content content--light content--beveled" id="about-me">
    <div class="content__inner">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <h2 class="content__heading">Adela Ticha</h2>
                <p>
                    When our family welcomed a new member Robin in September 2019, I&nbsp;realized it was the best time to jump into my old passion - <big><strong>graphic&nbsp;design</strong></big>. 
                </p>
                <p> 
                    Now during my maternity leave, I&nbsp;enjoy working in Inkscape and building logos for various projects.
                </p>
                <p>
                    I like to learn about those projects. I&nbsp;am good at pointing out unique facts and use them for logo design. I&nbsp;am also focused on detail.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                <img class="img-fluid d-none d-md-inline shadow-lg rounded-lg" src="../images/profile-picture-1000x850.jpg" alt="My Photo" width="500" height="425">
                <img class="img-fluid d-md-none shadow rounded" src="../images/profile-picture-680x578.jpg" alt="My Photo" width="340" height="298">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="content content--bg content--beveled" id="my-work">
    <div class="content__inner">
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-12">
                <h2 class="content__heading">My Work</h2>
            </div>
            {% for date, client in clients %}
              {% if not client.hidden %}
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                    <div class="portfolio">
                        <img class="img-fluid d-md-none" width="{{ clientHeadPictureSizes.sm.x }}"
					    	height="{{ clientHeadPictureSizes.sm.y }}" alt="{{ client.name }}"
							src="{{ client.image }}-sm.jpg?">
                        <img class="img-fluid d-none d-md-inline" width="{{ clientHeadPictureSizes.md.x }}"
					    	height="{{ clientHeadPictureSizes.md.y }}" alt="{{ client.name }}"
							src="{{ client.image }}-md.jpg?">
                        <div class="overlay">
                            <h2>{{ client.name }}</h2>
                            <h3>{{ client.type }}</h3>
                            <a class="info js-open-modal" href="{{ client.link }}">Show more</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
              {% endif %}
			{% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
